document_data.mainbody:
Noble Artificer Yanneth Kerigg was the high priest of the House of Wonders, a temple dedicated to Gond, in Urmlaspyr in 1358 DR.
Yanneth was the leader of Gonds faithful in Urmlaspyr. His congregation within the temple consisted of 16 other priests and 6 followers. Yanneth was personally known for his exquisite crafstmanship for weapons.
